Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.57,0:00:04.98,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,What's up with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:06.29,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,This is unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.67,0:00:09.80,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Tsumugi isn't normally gone for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.40,0:00:12.37,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Do you think something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.37,0:00:13.75,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Is she in trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.75,0:00:15.68,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Nah, no way. That can't be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.15,0:00:20.24,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Maybe she got embarrassed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.24,0:00:23.02,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,now that you're officially dating, Pairi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.02,0:00:23.85,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.51,0:00:27.65,Flashback - Italics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I love you, Hairi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.94,0:00:31.92,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,But I told her I loved her too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:32.57,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.48,0:00:34.36,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.38,0:00:36.80,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:40.79,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I was going to tell you \Nwhen all of us were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,0:00:43.70,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,I'm really happy for you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:46.75,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,You'd better make her happy, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.69,0:00:48.63,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.63,0:00:50.91,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Kind of a shame, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.91,0:00:56.09,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Now I'll have to share her boobies \Nwith you once they grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.09,0:00:57.17,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.17,0:01:00.84,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I-I mean, Tsumugi's boobs belong to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.84,0:01:02.60,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Not to anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.60,0:01:06.10,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,M-Maybe Tsumugi just slept in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.10,0:01:09.33,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Fine. Let's go get her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:14.15,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,She said she lives at the lighthouse.\NBut where does she really live?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.15,0:01:14.99,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.45,0:01:16.99,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.07,0:01:22.70,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Well, I've always met her \Nand parted ways with her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.30,0:01:26.16,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,She always sees me off from here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.04,0:01:34.32,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Hairi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.88,0:01:37.37,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,O-Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.37,0:03:10.98,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Excuse us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:12.63,Default,Grandma,0,0,0,,Yes, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:14.00,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:16.19,Default,Grandma,0,0,0,,Oh, good timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.06,0:03:18.81,Default,Grandma,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.81,0:03:20.03,Default,Grandma,0,0,0,,What you asked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.15,0:03:24.07,Default,Grandma,0,0,0,,It came in surprisingly quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:26.37,Default,Grandma,0,0,0,,Must be the power of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.95,0:03:32.50,Default,Grandma,0,0,0,,Maybe she was spirited away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:34.96,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Spirited away, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.38,0:03:37.62,Default,Grandma,0,0,0,,It was decades ago now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.62,0:03:39.71,Default,Grandma,0,0,0,,There was a real uproar about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.12,0:03:43.16,Default,Grandma,0,0,0,,A blonde girl up and vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.98,0:03:45.22,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,A blonde girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.69,0:03:49.86,Default,Grandma,0,0,0,,The whole island helped \Nher parents look for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.86,0:03:52.10,Default,Grandma,0,0,0,,but she never turned up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.49,0:03:58.49,Default,Grandma,0,0,0,,One boy kept searching desperately\N for her, just like you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:04:00.99,Default,Grandma,0,0,0,,I think he was the lighthouse keeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:02.66,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,The lighthouse keeper...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.66,0:04:06.53,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Is there anyone else who knew \Nthe girl that got spirited away?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:07.78,Default,Grandma,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:09.25,Default,Grandma,0,0,0,,Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.25,0:04:15.20,Default,Grandma,0,0,0,,Katou-san was the last one who knew her,\N and she passed away just recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:18.88,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,That sure was a shock to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.26,0:04:20.96,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,The spirited away business.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.96,0:04:26.47,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Pairi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:28.75,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Could you take a look at this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.73,0:04:31.92,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Tsumugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.42,0:04:33.60,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,But this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.97,0:04:35.58,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:36.92,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,It can't be, could it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:39.23,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,This is such an old photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.57,0:04:41.33,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Say something, Hairi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.85,0:04:43.27,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.27,0:04:46.71,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,But I can't stop thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.78,0:04:54.25,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,I've seen this somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.62,0:04:58.17,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Look. See?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.60,0:05:00.21,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I've seen this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:04.56,Flashback - Italics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Someone powerful used to live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.56,0:05:06.97,Flashback - Italics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,No one lives there anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:09.72,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Is this Tsumugi's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.05,0:05:14.89,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Pardon us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.37,0:05:21.43,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Maybe no one's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.43,0:05:24.07,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Hey, Tsumugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:32.58,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Looks like a girl's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.93,0:05:44.93,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Hairi-kun! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:48.84,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\shad0\bord0\c&H3C3733&\pos(320,149.02)}Tsumugi Wenders
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:48.84,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Tsumugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.65,0:05:52.97,Flashback - Italics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I started school on the island today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:57.98,Flashback - Italics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Everyone whispers about\N the color of my hair and eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:06:01.98,Flashback - Italics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,So my only friends are my stuffed animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.33,0:06:03.65,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Stuffed animals?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:06.82,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Were those...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.19,0:06:10.74,Flashback - Italics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,No one talked to me again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:12.83,Flashback - Italics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I think they're afraid of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.25,0:06:15.95,Flashback - Italics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,They must think I'm something like a namahage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:19.87,Flashback - Italics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,So I'm going to work up \Nthe courage to talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:23.04,Flashback - Italics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Like a namahage!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:25.40,Flashback,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Bring me the crying children!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:27.42,Flashback,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Bring me the naughty children!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:31.26,Flashback,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Bring me the disobedient children!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.53,0:06:40.19,Flashback - Italics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,It didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.78,0:06:58.73,Flashback - Italics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I've made a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:00.17,Flashback - Italics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Her name is Katou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.17,0:07:02.45,Flashback - Italics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,She's interested in stuffed animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.45,0:07:04.17,Flashback - Italics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,That makes me happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.66,0:07:06.55,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Good for you, Tsumugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.93,0:07:12.37,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Sounds like she made lots of friends, got \Nused to the island, and lived here happily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.51,0:07:16.70,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Tsumugi was going to elope \Nwith the lighthouse keeper...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:17.68,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.25,0:07:32.33,Flashback - Italics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I've decided to leave the island with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.33,0:07:34.20,Flashback - Italics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,We're meeting at the lighthouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.94,0:07:37.94,Flashback - Italics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Father, Mother, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.94,0:07:40.83,Flashback - Italics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,And to everyone on the island, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:42.96,Flashback - Italics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I love you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.37,0:07:46.04,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Could it be you're jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:47.09,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.09,0:07:48.58,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,You're true to yourself, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.58,0:07:53.18,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,S-Still, this is all stuff that\N happened decades ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:55.14,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,But eloping...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:07:59.86,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,I wonder if that's what really became of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.86,0:08:01.70,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,No, it wasn't that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:04.45,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Remember what the \Ngranny at the candy store said?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.45,0:08:08.29,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,The lighthouse keeper was looking \Nfor the missing girl too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.29,0:08:10.97,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,What, so she was actually spirited away then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.36,0:08:13.74,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:15.92,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,Was our Tsumugi also...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.03,0:08:22.70,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,There's more to this journal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.70,0:08:27.71,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\fs16\shad0\bord3\fnArial\an7\c&H373B3D&\3c&HB2B6B6&\b1}Tsumugi-chan is missing.\NTsumugi-chan won't come home.\NEveryone went to look for her.\NBut they couldn't find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.71,0:08:29.68,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.21,0:08:36.84,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\fs16\shad0\bord3\fnArial\an7\c&H373B3D&\3c&HB2B6B6&\b1}I'm so sad for Tsumugi-chan.\NPlease don't forget Tsumugi-chan, everyone.\NThat's my hope.\NSo I'll make sure no one forgets Tsumugi-chan.\NI have to make it sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:38.39,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.64,0:08:47.65,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.37,0:08:49.65,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Shizuku...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:52.10,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,The more we look for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.10,0:08:54.15,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,the more we look into this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.44,0:08:57.92,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,The more I feel like \Nwe'll never see her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.59,0:09:01.16,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Sorry, can I leave you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:02.51,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Hairi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.51,0:09:05.17,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,There's somewhere I need to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.13,0:09:23.06,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,You're all waiting for her too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:25.07,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,Same goes for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.07,0:09:30.98,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,All I can do is sit here and wait \Nfor Tsumugi to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:31.82,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:33.07,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.93,0:09:35.11,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Tsumugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.11,0:09:38.59,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Huh? Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:50.02,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:54.40,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,This isn't Tsumugi's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.21,0:10:03.06,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,What in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:06.15,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Wh-What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:11.67,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,It won't open.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:12.69,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:25.08,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.61,0:10:27.50,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I was going up just now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.98,0:10:38.51,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.51,0:10:39.54,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:45.44,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.52,0:10:47.77,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Tsumugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:48.95,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.95,0:10:50.64,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,We were worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.64,0:10:53.19,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I've been here the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.19,0:10:54.58,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.58,0:10:58.07,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,But I've been looking for you all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.89,0:11:02.11,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,You are... Tsumugi, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.11,0:11:06.31,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Indeed. I am most certainly Tsumugi Wenders.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:15.58,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Bring me the crying children!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:18.34,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Bring me the naughty children!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.34,0:11:21.51,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Bring me the disobedient children!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.51,0:11:25.14,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,H-How do you know about my \Nembarrassing introduction?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:26.96,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,You're joking...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.86,0:11:30.35,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I've been spirited away too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.86,0:11:40.28,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I wanna go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.28,0:11:44.56,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I seriously wanna go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.56,0:11:46.59,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Is this really going to get me home?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.59,0:11:49.58,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,It seemed to do the trick for everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:54.03,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I've never returned, so I wouldn't \Nknow if it works or not myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:12:01.34,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, anyone held here\N by something is stuck here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.92,0:12:08.26,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,And for so long that we don't \Neven know what holds us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.26,0:12:09.85,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,What holds you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:11.84,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,So you're stuck too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:16.52,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Do I look that much like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:18.80,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Like your, er...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:19.86,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Tsumugi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.74,0:12:24.66,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're shockingly identical.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.66,0:12:27.30,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Her personality is totally different, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:30.84,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,She's more lively and more committed \Nonce she puts her mind to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.84,0:12:32.98,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,So you kinda have to keep an eye on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:34.38,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.38,0:12:36.29,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I hope you get back to her soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.03,0:12:41.91,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I understand well how you feel, Takahara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:49.00,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I've long been separated from \Nmy lover and my dear friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.00,0:12:51.28,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,You mean the man you wanted to elope with?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.38,0:12:56.85,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I couldn't choose that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.20,0:13:01.25,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I grew scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.41,0:13:10.29,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I'd decided that, in order \Nto live with the man I love,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.29,0:13:13.87,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I would abandon my parents \Nand the people of the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.34,0:13:16.37,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,But I ended up hesitating,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:18.26,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,and I couldn't make up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:27.23,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Then, before I knew it, I was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.23,0:13:31.16,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I must still be hesitating.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:32.22,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Tsumugi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:37.26,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,But you came here in search \Nof someone you long for, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.26,0:13:40.46,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I'm sure that if you think \Nstrong thoughts of her,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:43.28,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,you'll be able to return to your world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.81,0:13:46.11,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Strong thoughts...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.11,0:13:48.02,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Please believe strongly in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:49.58,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,In your lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.20,0:13:52.28,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:54.66,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,No matter who she is,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.01,0:13:56.71,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,no matter her past...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.05,0:13:58.74,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.25,0:14:01.71,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,Right now, I simply miss her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.45,0:14:04.05,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,I want to see her smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.62,0:14:06.59,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,I want to hear her song.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.64,0:14:13.25,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,That song...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:15.18,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,That takes me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.03,0:14:22.27,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,A breeze...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:25.82,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,There might be an exit, Tsumugi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.50,0:14:29.92,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I'm still hesitating.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:32.28,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,If I go, the exit will surely vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.72,0:14:34.93,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,You'll have to go alone, Takahara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:35.70,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:43.79,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Please take good care of Tsumugi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:46.86,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.43,0:14:48.55,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.84,0:14:53.30,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,What are you doing up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:56.13,Flashback,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I'm looking for something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:14:58.06,Flashback,Hairi,0,0,0,,What are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.45,0:15:00.44,Flashback,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:01.65,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,Tsumugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:06.16,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,When you said you were looking \Nfor yourself, did you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:16.93,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.26,0:15:36.69,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Paringles are indestructible,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:37.97,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.85,0:15:40.15,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Tsumugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.26,0:15:47.23,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Hairi-kun! Hairi-kun! Hairi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.32,0:15:51.95,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Hairi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.36,0:15:56.30,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,God!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.30,0:15:58.02,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Where were you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:15:59.20,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Shizuku...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.86,0:16:01.91,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,First Tsumugi disappears...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.91,0:16:04.05,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,If you disappeared too...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.05,0:16:06.67,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,What would I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.79,0:16:08.94,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.51,0:16:11.49,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Where's Tsumugi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.60,0:16:14.75,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Hairi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.36,0:16:17.82,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.82,0:16:21.15,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Thank goodness, Hairi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.15,0:16:22.32,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Tsumugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.61,0:16:26.19,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,The day after we parted ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:31.31,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,I was waiting at the lighthouse \Nin case Tsumugi came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.17,0:16:37.93,Flashback,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Shizuku, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.03,0:16:42.54,Flashback,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Tsumugi! Tsumugi! Tsumugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.43,0:16:49.11,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,But right as Tsumugi came back,\N you vanished next.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:51.18,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,I was so worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.18,0:16:52.13,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.35,0:16:55.88,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:57.89,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Tsumugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.59,0:17:01.81,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Tsumugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.81,0:17:03.78,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,D-Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.78,0:17:07.81,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,You're going to get my \Ntears and snot on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:09.11,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:16.36,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I want to stay like this \Nfor a little longer, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.85,0:17:19.24,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Sheesh, you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.65,0:17:21.03,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Both of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:32.59,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I was gone a whole day?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.59,0:17:33.83,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,You were.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.83,0:17:35.77,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Where exactly where you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.77,0:17:36.93,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:38.05,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:43.18,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.18,0:17:44.09,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Mugyu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.09,0:17:45.10,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,What gives?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.10,0:17:46.49,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:48.52,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I don't remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.01,0:17:53.11,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Mugyu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.27,0:18:00.70,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Not much we can do\Nif you don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.27,0:18:04.45,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:05.57,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:08.41,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.41,0:18:09.96,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.62,0:18:13.16,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,You had me all sorts of worried,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.16,0:18:15.01,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,but I'm just glad you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.43,0:18:17.28,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:18.22,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Where's Umi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:21.02,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,She worried herself to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.02,0:18:23.22,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,Go apologize to her in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.22,0:18:24.42,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.42,0:18:27.10,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,Tsumugi-chan, it's late now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:28.72,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,Why don't you stay the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:31.13,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Mugyu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:42.77,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Hairi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.75,0:18:45.52,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,May I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:47.88,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.88,0:18:48.76,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.83,0:18:57.30,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Could we talk for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.43,0:19:06.49,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,You know how I said I'm leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:12.07,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,It's not that I'm going home \Nor abroad or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:13.80,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.74,0:19:15.76,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.25,0:19:18.92,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Mugyu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:20.53,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Listen, Tsumugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.53,0:19:24.40,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I don't mind whether you \Ntell me about that or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.46,0:19:26.94,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:32.08,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I'm going to spend my time \Nwith you until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.40,0:19:36.80,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Whether you tell me anything \Nor you don't, I'll be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.81,0:19:40.09,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Hairi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:48.13,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I want to be with you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.13,0:19:50.98,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Stay with me until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.98,0:19:51.92,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.76,0:19:56.98,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,There's something I have to tell you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.48,0:20:00.71,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I met Tsumugi Wenders-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.50,0:20:06.30,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I don't remember where I was,\N but that part, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.84,0:20:08.74,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I get the sense that I have to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.24,0:20:13.19,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Did Tsumugi-chan seem well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:14.05,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.05,0:20:15.49,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,She did seem well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.49,0:20:16.79,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,She did, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.79,0:20:17.92,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.06,0:20:19.92,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.20,0:20:22.81,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,When you said you were \Nlooking for yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.81,0:20:24.34,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Did you mean her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.34,0:20:25.14,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.14,0:20:26.43,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,That's Tsumugi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.34,0:20:31.68,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Are you going back to her \Nat the end of the summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:33.34,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:40.58,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Now that you've found her for me,\N I think I can return to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.58,0:20:44.32,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Good thing too, since she must be lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.83,0:20:47.09,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,That's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.23,0:20:50.83,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I'll be lonely too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.44,0:20:53.98,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Mugyu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:56.54,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,P-Please don't be so selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:20:58.71,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I'm going to miss you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.71,0:21:03.33,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I won't know what to do if you say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.31,0:21:05.68,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:09.01,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,For you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.78,0:21:14.77,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Shizuku told me that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.77,0:21:18.73,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,a gift is the best way to express \Nyourself to someone you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.73,0:21:21.27,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Shizuku always knows best!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.27,0:21:23.70,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,May I put it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.70,0:21:24.64,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.02,0:21:33.04,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:35.20,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,It looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.10,0:21:41.46,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I can tell what it means to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.92,0:22:04.80,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,One week remained until August 31st.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.44,0:22:09.13,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,Our summer was about to end.

